## `summary_writer.py` — what it collects

Reads from all `MD_run_*/analysis.log` and `MD_run_*/rdf_process.log` and writes `summary.txt`:

```
Run         Carrier   Count   Volume(m³)   Ea(eV)   D0(cm²/s)   σ@300K(S/m)   Bulk(GPa)   Shear(GPa)   Young(GPa)   Poisson
MD_run_1    Li        111     2.19e-27     0.32      1.4e-4       3.2e-2        ...
```

Plus per-pair CN table from RDF logs.

